Enum MediaPlayerEventType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<MediaPlayerEventType>
      uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player.events.MediaPlayerEventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MediaPlayerEventType>
public enum MediaPlayerEventType
extends java.lang.Enum<MediaPlayerEventType>

Enumeration of media player event bit-masks.

The event flag masks should be considered private implementation and are subject to change.
